{
  "stem": "21437.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the 1st of September, 1939, when it broke out, when I came from school, I was told that we are going to leave, and immediately, straight away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to my mother, seeing that before, I was sometimes standing where the trains are passing and the Jewish people are coming from Germany, passing through this town.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just had one bundle with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was always-- I had something over my arm and always was it flowers, or food, or a book, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was always asking them about books, you know, if they have books?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened with their books?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, just one book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to my mother, and what will-- Mom, how can I leave?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What will happen with my friends?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, the same what will happen with you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, no, I mean my books.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How can I go and leave my books behind?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She said, one book, just one book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What book did you take?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took-- would you believe it that I can't-- I took a book",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "that was in Latin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked my mother-- that was Sienkiewicz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked my mother when I was very little, what does quo vadis mean?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, quo vadis domino, which means, interpreted, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], which means in English, what are you aiming at?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you trying to accomplish?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or better, what are you trying to accomplish, human being?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought, again, you know, whatever I needed, I went to my mother, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that she knew how to answer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what happened next when you were told you were leaving?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, next, we were in a haphazard way, what I thought that it was a haphazard way.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
